<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Business Compliance Services - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link class="stylesheet" rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>

    <section class="page-header page-header-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Business Compliance Services</h1>
        <p>Professional, reliable compliance reporting to keep your UK business on solid footing with HMRC and Companies
          House.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-detail services-page">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="services-grid" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">

          <!-- Bookkeeping -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-book"></i></div>
              <h2>Bookkeeping</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Accurate, real-time records are the foundation of healthy business decisions. We maintain your ledgers
                on daily,
                weekly, or monthly basis, ensuring that your accounts are always up-to-date, organized and audit-ready.
              </p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>

                <li>Receipt processing via cloud-based tools such as Dext, Hubdoc</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Statutory Accounts -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
              <h2>Statutory Accounts</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Year-end statutory accounts prepared in accordance with UK GAAP/FRS with filling submitted to Companies
                House and HMRC, as required.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Preparation of Balance Sheets and Profit & Loss Accounts</li>
                <li>Preparation of statutory notes and directors' reports</li>
                <li>Reconciliation of balance sheet control accounts</li>
                <li>Electronic filing of statutory accounts with companies House</li>
                <li>Review of Year-end adjustments and accounting disclosures</li>

              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Corp Tax -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-percent"></i></div>
              <h2>Corporation Tax</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Ensure your company files accurate CT600 returns. We analyse your expenses and capital expenditure to
                optimise available tax reliefs and allowances, while ensuring full compliance with HMRC requirements.
              </p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Corporation Tax computation and CT600 preparation</li>
                <li>Capital allowances reviews and claims, including Annual Investments Allowance(AIA)
                </li>
                <li>R&D tax relief reviews and claim preparation, where eligible</li>
                <li>Quarterly installment payment support, where applicable</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>


          <!-- Payroll & Pensions -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-people-carry-box"></i></div>
              <h2>Payroll and Pensions</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Ensure your employees are paid accurately, securely, and on time. We provide complete payroll services,
                including weekly or monthly processing and full workplace pension compliance.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Real Time Information (RTI) submissions to HMRC</li>
                <li>Custom payslip generation and distribution</li>
                <li>Auto-enrolment setup and workplace pension compliance (including NEST, Smart-Pension, and other
                  providers)</li>
                <li>Preparation of P60s and P45s, and management of student loan deduction</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- VAT Returns -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
              <h2>VAT Returns</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Accurate VAT Return preparation and filing, ensuring compliance, while helping you benefit from the
                most
                suitable VAT scheme for your business.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>VAT return preparation and filing</li>
                <li>VAT scheme assessment, including Cash Accounting, Flat Rate, and Annual Accounting Schemes</li>
                <li>Partial exemption calculations and advisory support</li>
                <li>HMRC VAT inquiry and compliance support</li>
                <li>VAT registration, deregistration and ongoing Compliance guidance</li>

              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Making Tax Digital -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-cloud-arrow-up"></i></div>
              <h2>Making Tax Digital</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Navigate Making Tax Digital with confidence. We help your business adapt compliance digital systems,
                maintain accurate digital records and ensuring all digital links meet HMRC requiremnets. </p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>MTD software setup and implementation</li>
                <li>Review of digital record keeping and MTD Compliance</li>
                <li>MTD for Income Tax Self Assessment (ITSA) preparation and advisory support</li>
                <li>Ongoing MTD compliance guidance and training</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>


        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Comprehensive Business Compliance?</h2>
        <p>Let's design a structured compliance package for your company.</p>
        <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>

</html>